With time, the Teachers Service Commission has empowered boards of management to initiate discipline procedures against suspected head teachers within the confines of properly constituted meetings thus saving parents the previous archaic practice locking offices.
The protest by lecturers at Egerton University against the return of the vice-chancellor through a court order is shocking. This happening within the same year that the University of Nairobi had a protracted process of recruiting the current Vice Chancellor is serious cause for concern in the sector. Moi University had had a similar situation few years earlier.



